# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Desi Connect USA — Docker Ignore
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Dependencies (installed inside container)
node_modules
**/node_modules

# Build outputs (rebuilt inside container)
**/dist
**/build
**/.next

# Test & coverage
**/coverage
**/__tests__
**/tests
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
jest.config.*

# Git
.git
.gitignore

# IDE
.vscode
.idea
*.swp
*.swo

# Environment (secrets injected at runtime)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# CI/CD
.github

# Docker (don't recurse)
docker-compose*.yml

# Documentation
*.md
LICENSE
docs/

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
